---
title: Italian Panzanella with Cannellini Beans, Fresh Mozzarella, and Summer Veggies
description: Whoever came up with the idea of tossing bread into salads was a genius. Not only does it absorb the dressing, but it adds a hearty crunch to this colorful vegetarian dish. For an extra kick of flavor, let the salad sit for 10 minutes before digging in.
